channel.title: What is wrong with Mopar SERVERS!
channel.description:
Every server i put up, everything i use here...dosent work!
Ive tried the same thing which says Error Connecting to Server. Must be down. Click "cancel" then "Start Server" to make your own.
WHY DOES IT DO THIS TO ME HAS GOD SET UPON A CURSE!
Help, homefry

item.title: What is wrong with Mopar SERVERS!
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

You sound pretty hopeless. =\

Either their server is offline.
They require you to be in the Hamachi network with them.
Or you’re putting in the incorrect IP address.

I’d say it’d be one of the first two.
